==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Embronze
<hw>Em*bronze"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
embody in bronze; to set up a bronze representation of, as of a
person.</def> <mark>[Poetic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To color in imitation of bronze. See
<er>Bronze</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Embrothel</ent>⟦br⟧
